    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its 8,000 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. This example delivers exceptional throttle response and a linear torque curve, paired with a precise 6-speed manual gearbox and a functional M-Variable differential lock. Key preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS system refresh and reinforcement of the rear subframe mounting points to ensure structural rigidity under high lateral loads. The chassis remains composed with a well-sorted suspension setup, providing the communicative steering feel and balanced 50/50 weight distribution characteristic of this platform. This is a performance-ready specimen optimized for the discerning enthusiast who prioritizes drivetrain health and chassis dynamics.",
